data.description: Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough. Welcome to this exquisite home nestled in a charming community surrounded by multiple parks, playgrounds, and lakes. Inside, you'll find a meticulously designed space with no carpet throughout, ensuring easy maintenance. The open floor plan of the main living area seamlessly connects the spacious kitchen, featuring granite counters, a large island, and ample cabinet space, to the dining area and living room. The home also boasts an office for those who work from home and a generously-sized game room, which can be easily adapted to suit your interests. The primary bedroom is a sanctuary with its tall ceilings and includes an ensuite bath complete with dual sinks, a luxurious soaking tub, and a walk-in closet, providing both convenience and comfort. The backyard is fully fenced for privacy and it features a large covered patio where you can relax and entertain while appreciating beautiful outdoor weather.
